posts.body:
>interior design
cyberpunk = high tech, low life.
gotta define low life first.
does it mean ikea/target/walmart box diy furniture?
does it mean yard sale/handmedowns/found on street?
is it some combination?
two things to pay attention to are location, which in the case of redecoration is out of your hands, and lighting, which is in your hands. 
it probably becomes autistic when you have light up displays/signs, especially corp related memorabilia
